{"tid":1701272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要選！選舉一取消，香港人就輸到貼地！","createTime":"2019-11-09T03:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T03:33:59.000Z","uid":163023,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"231d169516e98c4c0b6f142eade1da9f80d01a00","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"五個月嚟全港真香港人出錢出力，花心機花時間，喊過痛過，連人命都保唔住。<br />\n一切惡夢源頭都係制度嘅不公義。<br />\n宜家班保皇黨、建制派為咗保住份糧，保住條命想叫停選舉令自己留喺議會！佢地要買人頭、買票、製造輿論壓力去阻止議會選舉，其實真係預咗。班垃圾有咩做唔出？香港人就同佢鬥多人，鬥齊心！<br />\n<br />\n香港人一定要透過選舉，借呢個合法、無死角嘅方法建立一個爲真正香港人服務嘅議會政制。去大大力制裁呢個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺人政府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以用盡方法保住個選舉，輸埋就被清算，乜都無架啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#香港人報仇"},{"pid":"5cdbcd135e91c109ad781529654f4f0805caa3d8","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"cf930699ed5387f28ec0296e4aadd5a7470acd73","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c4503fe452271e6ebac885c6af4165082f5b2ab6","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"46e97a584dff2f5ccdfe4c653ce1101406bc895f","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:14:40.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"434fb8aa367cbb4811c156a5b70a6a81aa885b5e","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"4f46e960092721008d3e7c268c2aa098c1908855","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"60b086f11806be7969867e2d099908372811b95a","tid":1701272,"uid":163023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"bfad48ff2d7dc6a40cbd0f72ae9f561f8c2298ca","tid":1